data.description: GREENBELT. OVER .26 ACRES. 5 BEDROOMS. Imagine Living the Life...Designed with a relaxed traditional style. This amazing residence is overflowing with the finest of everything. Situated on an oversized corner-style homesite located within the neighborhood of Valley Ranch. Enter your home through a beautiful, custom crafted front door boasting gorgeous LVP throughout. Enjoy the elegantly styled kitchen that offers gas cooking and stainless appliances paired handsomely with white shaker style cabinets positioned with an open concept and island seating. The spacious primary retreat offers double vanities, walk-in closet & separate garden tub with walk in shower. A covered patio overlooks a serene green space with an entertainer's paradise for a backyard. No city taxes and Resort style amenities to enjoy Tennis, Basketball, Fishing, and Swimming. Don't forget about the onsite Gym! Schedule a showing today and prepare to fall in love with the harmonious blend of comfort, style, and entertainment that awaits you at this exceptional residence.
